31:07.074 --> 31:08.637
They were known for their giving.

31:08.677 --> 31:16.470
They were known for their generosity that overflowed and permeated everything that they did.

31:18.914 --> 31:21.960
They were known for their money and their giving patterns.

31:22.921 --> 31:25.125
And that's what made them a very crazy church.

31:25.766 --> 31:32.658
We tend not to get a lot of teaching these days in the North American church about money because it makes people mad.

31:33.442 --> 31:39.950
I've yet to find a person that was offended by teaching on money who was faithful to the church and giving money.

31:40.911 --> 31:48.240
People that mostly are offended are those that don't faithfully participate in an active worship that we call generosity.

31:49.702 --> 31:55.909
But I've to come to discover in my journey that a missionary church is a giving church.

31:57.351 --> 31:59.013
Salem Fields has a reputation.

31:59.493 --> 32:03.378
